text: Is anyone from HS here to help with an API limit issue? Our client upgraded to get more lists in HS yet the API is still stopping them at the 1,000 limit.
I tried support and they simply told me to reach out to the CAM on the account

hey <@U2H3TT8F2>, i’m pretty sure we have a max of 1,000 regardless of how you upgrade: <https://knowledge.HubSpot.com/articles/kcs_article/lists/lists-faq>. see the section titled “Is there a limit on how many lists I can have in HubSpot?”

Was there a form or something that was filled out to get access to more? From what I know I don’t think this is possible.
